This latest addition to IMAGES' 21st Century series brings together more than 50 of the world's most stylish contemporary houses from around the world (including 10 stunning Australian projects). 

From the Adriatic Coast in Greece, to the rugged mountains of Switzerland; from the suburbs of Japan, to the glittering views from the Hollywood Hills, this diverse selection of modern houses have all been designed by some of the best residential architects working today. 

Complete with stunning professional colour photography, floor plans and enlightening project descriptions, 21st Century Architecture: Designer Houses will be of interest to anyone interested in beautiful houses, those who are looking for inspiration and those who like to dream.


By Mark Cleary
Published by Images Publishing Group in 2013
PDF, Retail, 225 pages, English
